collections.name: Urban Tarot
collections.description:
Urban Tarot Collection – A Fusion of Mysticism & Street Culture
Step into a world where ancient mysticism meets the raw energy of the city. The Urban Tarot Collection is a bold reimagining of traditional tarot, infused with the grit, color, and rhythm of modern street life. Each card transforms classic archetypes into powerful urban icons—figures adorned in streetwear, graffiti-covered thrones, neon-lit alleyways, and towering cityscapes that pulse with energy.
This collection blends spirituality with contemporary culture, capturing the essence of resilience, creativity, and transformation found in urban environments. Whether you’re a tarot reader, a collector, or an NFT enthusiast, Urban Tarot offers a fresh perspective on divination, where magic is woven into the streets.

collections.name: Theories as Medicine
collections.description: Theories as Medicine, an NFT collection where concepts transcend into visual poetry and elusive cures. Each piece radiates an inner force — a medicinal essence crafted within, tailored to the beholder’s spirit. Whether forged in fact or born of reverie, these theories wield influence, melding reality and illusion into a vivid tapestry. Who arbitrates truth in art? Every mind can conceive a theory, yet only the intrepid harness the sublime remedy latent in us all. These creations are more than images — they’re cryptic vessels of thought, pulsing with mysteries that beckon the bold to decode their depths. Dare you seize their veiled power?
